{"tid":2078707,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解賭錢係犯法？","createTime":"2020-06-25T08:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T09:14:05.000Z","uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"15dddf038d2d8fcae4e2ee46aa47d58bf9a257cf","tid":2078707,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"冇刑毀冇傷人冇阻礙社會安寧？<br />\n<br />\n有冇法律人士講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在家裡賭博有什麼限制？<br />\n<br />\n在家的社交場合中進行的博彩遊戲，只要不是以生意形式經營，以及除了在博彩贏錢以外沒有再賺取利益（如俗稱&ldquo;抽佣&rdquo;或 &ldquo;抽水&rdquo;等行為），便屬合法。"},{"pid":"2da01c554f6623fd22051cb31d7f6f0534f880d2","tid":2078707,"uid":20924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"政府無稅收"},{"pid":"03eb865e7f4840aee6cfaabd9fcc78abf3e5ed9c","tid":2078707,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"我怎麼知道在一間場所賭博是否合法？<br />\n<br />\n在以下處所的社交場合中進行博彩遊戲是合法的：<br />\n<br />\n獲發酒樓牌照的處所；獲發賣酒牌照的處所；或有牌會社。<br />\n<br />\n但這些處所的經營模式必須與以下規則相符：<br />\n<br />\n進入該場所不必繳費；處所負責人（如經理）並沒有參與遊戲；博彩遊戲中不涉及與莊家對賭；以及博彩遊戲非為任何人獲取私利而進行（博彩者贏得的錢除外），但處所可以向玩家收取租用牌的規定費用。"},{"pid":"1ee00c36ed0fb6c3765fb628d045d8e245dac1f6","tid":2078707,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2da01c554f6623fd22051cb31d7f6f0534f880d2","tid":2078707,"uid":20924,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:55:36.000Z","msg":"政府無稅收"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:56:36.000Z","msg":"我都諗緊呢個先係主要問題<br />\n<br />\n咁咪仲似商業問題<br />\n<br />\n多過治安問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc59111dc6047c79b8f6eaeeb8a4f3db2fae8ad","tid":2078707,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"有莊家就犯法"},{"pid":"383dbf